                     </persName>
                     
                   who had served as a soldier on board the Eurus, and that certain prize money was due to him at the time of his death, that he the said 
                     <persName id="t18061029-53-person579">
                        Joseph 
                        Knight
                     <interp inst="t18061029-53-person579" type="surname" value="Knight"></interp>
