             sworn. Examined by Mr. Reynolds. You are a clerk of the check office at Greenwich hospital. - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Is that your signature. - A. It is my signature. It is a certificate of the money of the prize that was due to 
               <persName id="t18061029-53-person601">
